# Web3Forms public access key for the contact form (PLAN.md §5).
# Public by design — safe to ship in the built HTML. Get one (no account
# needed for the free tier) at https://web3forms.com and set the destination
# email on their dashboard against this key (the TODO_EMAIL launch item).
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the value before building for production.
PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
